      <title>美联储主席戴利谈利率政策和经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/fed-s-daly-on-rate-policy-and-growth-forecast-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽·戴利表示，现在是调整货币政策的时候了，现在判断未来降息的速度还为时过早。她在彭博电视台与迈克·麦基进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/fed-s-daly-on-rate-policy-and-growth-forecast-video</guid>
